    <item>
      <title>世界银行私人金融部门董事总经理认为投资将转向新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/ifc-s-diop-on-investment-into-emerging-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际金融公司的 Makhtar Diop 认为，随着货币宽松周期的持续，过去一年流入非经合组织国家的外国直接投资放缓的趋势可能最终会有所转变。他与彭博电视台首席非洲主播兼记者 Jennifer Zabasajja 一起讨论了他和其他多边银行如何协同努力填补融资缺口。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-08/ifc-s-diop-on-investment-into-emerging-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:58:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vasle 称欧洲央行下周降息并不能保证 12 月利率变动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-cut-next-week-wouldn-t-guarantee-december-move-vasle-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员波斯扬·瓦斯莱 (Bostjan Vasle) 表示，10 月份降低利率并不意味着欧洲央行一定会在今年最后一次会议上再次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-cut-next-week-wouldn-t-guarantee-december-move-vasle-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:56:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国投资者购买菲律宾股票创十年来最高纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/foreign-buying-of-philippine-stocks-matches-best-run-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于菲律宾通胀的缓解带来了进一步降息的希望，海外投资者已连续 27 个交易日抢购菲律宾股票，创下十年来最长的连续买入纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/foreign-buying-of-philippine-stocks-matches-best-run-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 08:47:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
